<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf5a4c99-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11924"><num value="11924">§ 11924.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of this subchapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idbf5a4c9a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11924/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Controlled substance</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “controlled substance” has the meaning given such term in <ref href="/us/usc/t21/s802">section 802 of title 21</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idbf5a4c9b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11924/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idbf5a4c9c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/690/tV/s5145">Pub. L. 100–690, title V, § 5145</ref>, <date date="1988-11-18">Nov. 18, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/4304">102 Stat. 4304</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
